data.description: Serene, private and a nature lover's DREAM. Welcome to this custom built, secluded home situated on 3 acres of land with enamoring views! Home is nestled amidst trees sprinkled throughout the property. Back yard is perfect for a pool and/or garden. The wraparound porch has 360 mountain top views. 3 bedroom, 2.5 baths, with primary suite on the first floor. A breeze way connects the 2 car attached garage with another 2 car garage/workshop detached at the driveway. Entertain friends and family on the private back patio, while relaxing in the jacuzzi hot tub and serenaded by the sounds of the forest. One must see to appreciate the location and setting of this remarkable home. Over 2,040 SF of living space, this home is the perfect size for a family. New roof, HVAC, carpet, light fixtures and paint. Schedule your private showing today.
